data.description: Discover the perfect 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom corner unit townhome in picturesque Coral Springs. This two-story gem features a 2-car garage with tons of storage space and an open floor plan with a modern eat-in kitchen and dining area. With four spacious bedrooms, there's plenty of room for family, guests, or a home office. The master suite includes a en-suite bath with a large soaker tub, double vanity and glass enclosed shower for your comfort.     Situated in the heart of Coral Springs near Coral Spring Mall and The Walk, you'll enjoy proximity to shopping, dining, and parks. Don't miss the chance to call this townhome in the vibrant Coral Springs community of Royal Palm Village your own.
